## Error Handling

| Error | Cause | Solution |
|-------|-------|----------|
| Invalid API Key | Key not found or expired | Verify key in {{ display_name }} dashboard |
| Rate Limited | Exceeded API quota | Check limits at {{ docs_url | default('docs.' + company + '.com') }} |
| Network Error | Firewall blocking | Ensure outbound HTTPS (443) allowed |
| Module Not Found | SDK not installed | Run `npm install {{ npm_package | default(company + '-sdk') }}` |

